Wmns Terrex Swift R3 GTX 'Hazy Emerald'
Fresh Foam Roav Backpack 2E Wide 'Dark Blaze'

Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD 'Paint Splatter - White'
Wmns Ace Summerlite 'White Light Thistle'
results.story: The Nike women’s Ace Summerlite ‘White Light Thistle’ delivers a lightweight golf shoe that places a premium on comfort. A thin and flexible overlay reinforces a breathable white mesh upper tuned to the contours of the female foot, complete with a shallow toe box, tapered heel and a higher arch. Both the tongue and collar are lined in micro-suede to allow for barefoot wear. A plush foam midsole is undergirded by a rubber outsole with an integrated traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: Air Zoom Terra Kiger 7 'Light Bone Cargo Khaki'
Star Runner 2 PS 'Photon Dust Game Royal'
Team Hustle D10 GS 'Black Metallic Silver'
Air Max 90 PS 'Evolution of Icons'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Air Max 90 PS ‘Evolution of Icons’ celebrates the history of Air with a variety of vintage logos printed on the sockliner. The exterior build comprises a breathable white mesh base with grey suede overlays and a matching leather mudguard. Vibrant accents give a further nod to Air Max history, highlighted by Volt-colored eyelets, a turquoise Swoosh and Infrared cassette detailing around the visible Max Air unit. An added pink mini-Swoosh decorates the lateral forefoot.

results.name: Air Max Excee PS 'Pure Platinum Fuchsia Glow'
adidas Yeezy 500 High Frosted Blue
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 High ‘Frosted Blue’ showcases a contrasting two-tone color palette on a retro-inspired lifestyle sneaker that traces a lineage to the adidas KB8 III. The upper is composed of stretchy elastane in a vibrant blue finish, fortified with suede overlays in a lighter blue shade. They’re joined by tan suede on the sneaker’s segmented eyestay and reinforced toe wrap. Additional details include toggle lacing and a padded, high-cut collar. Cushioning arrives via a podular adiPRENE midsole that gives the nod to adidas’ Feet You Wear technology.

results.name: Wmns Flex Experience Run 10 'White Violet Shock'
Club C Revenge Legacy 'White Orange Flare'
Air Max SC PS 'White Game Royal'
Court Borough Low 2 Canvas GS 'Black Cork'
Flex Experience Run 10 Extra Wide 'Black White'
Wmns Gel Venture 8 'Carrier Grey Red Brick'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Venture 8 ‘Carrier Grey Red Brick’ features a durable lugged rubber outsole designed for running in the great outdoors. A black EVA midsole yields soft cushioning and a smooth ride, while a purple TPU shank plate delivers midfoot stability. Up top, breathable grey mesh is reinforced with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with black and red tiger stripes. Webbing straps integrated into the lacing system provides a feeling of lockdown.

results.name: Gel Cumulus 23 'Black'
results.story: The ASICS Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Black’ steps out in a sleek, monochromatic finish. The performance runner incorporates 20% recycled materials into the engineered mesh upper, accented with reflective detailing for added visibility in low-light conditions. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length FlyteFoam midsole, enhanced with visible Gel technology in the heel. Additionally, 3D Space Construction features strategically placed pillars within the midsole, resulting in improved compression and a smoother ride.

results.name: Wmns Gel Venture 8 'Black Sheet Rock'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Venture 8 ‘Black Sheet Rock’ highlights subtle pop of color on a running shoe designed for outdoor trails. The sneaker makes use of breathable black and white mesh throughout the upper, featuring a more accommodating toe box that allows for toe splay. Bright aqua accents land on webbing straps integrated into the lacing system, as well as a TPU shank in the lugged rubber outsole. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an EVA midsole with ASICS’ Gel technology in the heel.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Hierro v6 'Black Fig'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam Hierro v6 ‘Black Fig’ showcases muted earth tones on a rugged trail runner built to take on the elements. TPU threads are woven into the brown mesh upper for added support and protection in high-wear areas, while laser perforations deliver improved breathability. The lightweight build is mounted on a textured Fresh Foam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a lugged Vibram outsole for multi-directional traction.

results.name: Wmns Suede Classic 'International Women's Day'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Suede Classic ‘International Women’s Day’ celebrates the annual observance with a monochromatic pastel design. A soft lavender hue saturates the soft suede upper, accented with a tonal Formstrip and silver foil PUMA Suede branding on the lateral side panel. Mismatched lace jewels display PUMA’s jumping cat logo and ‘Girl Power’ script. A durable rubber cupsole, complete with distinctively textured sidewalls, maintains the sneaker’s one-note finish.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Broderie'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Broderie’ gives the foundational sneaker a lifted look, courtesy of an exaggerated EVA midsole with traditional license-plate branding and contrasting black pinstripes. The stacked tooling is underpinned by a standard brown rubber outsole with a customary diamond tread. Up top, cream-hued canvas is entirely covered in embroidered florals for a spring-ready look.

results.name: Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit 'White'
results.story: The Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit ‘White’ offers the creative’s pristine take on the vintage sneaker. White Primeknit is utilized on the upper, featuring woven construction that mimics the iconic shell toe. A small Trefoil tag in Vivid Green is added to the medial collar, matching an inverted adidas wordmark on the tongue and ‘Humanrace’ embroidered on the heel tab. Pharrell’s signature reflexology graphic adorns the sockliner. The low-top is mounted on a standard Superstar cupsole, complete with a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Five Ten Impact Pro Mid 'Black Red'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Impact Pro Mid ‘Black Red’ delivers a mountain biking shoe that can withstand wet and muddy conditions. Built with a mid-cut collar for added support and protection, the quick-drying synthetic upper is rendered in a sleek black finish with crimson Five Ten branding on the lateral quarter panel. A matching black finish is applied to a compression-molded polyurethane midsole, reinforced with a Stealth S1 Dotty tread outsole that ensures feet stay on the pedals.

results.name: FuelCell Propel RMX 2E Wide 'Cobalt Blue Team Gold'
results.story: The New Balance FuelCell Propel RMX 2E Wide ‘Cobalt Blue Team Gold’ pairs a progressive bootie-style upper with responsive tooling. The mesh and textile build is reinforced with no-sew overlays and a synthetic midfoot cage. On the lateral side, an outlined ‘N’ logo extends to the full-length FuelCell midsole, offering superior energy return and a feeling of forward propulsion. The outsole places NDurance rubber in high-wear areas for lightweight traction.

results.name: Deviate Nitro Elite 'White Lava Blast'
results.story: The PUMA Deviate Nitro Elite ‘White Lava Blast’ dresses the performance running shoe in a lightweight build that blends neutral tones with sharp bursts of color. A semi-translucent mono mesh upper is lined in synthetic suede and reinforced with a TPU heel counter. Reflective detailing around the collar offers added visibility in low-light conditions. Outlined in red, the signature Formstrip extends to the NITRO FOAM midsole, which is fitted with a carbon fiber INNOPLATE for maximum energy transfer at toe-off.

results.name: Future Rider 'Convey'
results.story: The PUMA Future Rider ‘Convey’ showcases subdued tones on a lifestyle runner modeled after the Fast Rider from 1980. Ivory-hued textile is accented with a white leather Formstrip and reinforced with stitch-down beige leather overlays at the forefoot and heel. ‘Every Difference’ is inscribed beneath the lateral eyestay. A bright red TPU insert on the lateral heel gives way to a lightweight injection-molded EVA midsole, supported underfoot by PUMA’s Federbein rubber outsole.

results.name: FuelCell Propel RMX 'Cobalt Blue Team Gold'
results.story: The New Balance FuelCell Propel RMX ‘Cobalt Blue Team Gold’ highlights vibrant hues on a performance running shoe built with high-rebound cushioning. The bootie-style upper, constructed from a blend of sandwich mesh, translucent textile and synthetic leather overlays, hugs the foot with seamless support. A full-length FuelCell midsole delivers energy return with each step. Underfoot, an NDurance rubber outsole supplies grippy traction in high-wear areas.

results.name: Wild Rider 'Layers - White Urban Red'
results.story: Inspired by the movement and energy of city life, the PUMA Wild Rider Layers ‘White Urban Red' showcases varied colors and textures on a retro-inspired build. The upper is constructed from breathable white nylon that’s reinforced with nubuck overlays in contrasting grey and blue finishes. PUMA’s signature Formstrip is rendered in PU-coated red leather that extends past the shaggy suede heel tab to form a functional pull tab. An injection-molded EVA midsole provides soft cushioning and a smooth ride.

results.name: Style Rider 'Convey'
results.story: The PUMA Style Rider ‘Convey’ features natural hues and materials, resulting in a stripped-down edition of the lifestyle silhouette inspired by the original Fast Rider. The grey textile upper is fortified with camel-colored suede overlays at the toe and heel, the latter embellished with a bright red gel insert. ‘Every Difference Makes a Difference’ is inscribed across the heel tabs of the left and right shoe. The sneaker rides on an injection-molded EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a studded Federbein outsole.

results.name: RS-X 'Convey'
results.story: The PUMA RS-X ‘Convey’ features a warm palette that combines natural hues with bright orange accents. Breathable textile is reinforced with overlays in tan suede and light brown nubuck, the latter featuring heel inscription that reads ‘Every difference makes a difference.’ Responsive cushioning is provided by a polyurethane midsole with geometric TPU pieces embedded in the sidewall. Underfoot, a solid rubber outsole offers durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'White Ivory Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘White Ivory Blue’ pairs classic tennis style with a modern, sustainable build. The white synthetic leather upper is made with 50% recycled content and features familiar perforated three-stripe branding on the side panels. An adidas Trefoil is stamped on the pale blue heel tab, while a contrasting beige tongue is marked with the iconic Stam Smith logo. The low-top rides on a durable rubber cupsole that’s unchanged from the original.

results.name: Vivienne Westwood x Gel Kayano 27 LTX 'Vapor'
results.story: The Vivienne Westwood x ASICS Gel Kayano 27 LTX ‘Vapor’ is drawn from a three-piece collection inspired by the British fashion designer’s latex stockings. The look of the rubber hosiery is channeled via the sneaker’s semi-translucent TPU shroud, finished in a monochromatic lavender hue and secured with zip closure. Dual branding on the lateral side includes Vivienne Westwood’s Orb Saturn logo. The streamlined assemblage is mounted on a FLYTEFOAM Propel midsole with visible Gel cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Vivienne Westwood x Gel Kayano 27 LTX 'Citrus'
results.story: The Vivienne Westwood x ASICS Gel Kayano 27 LTX ‘Citrus’ represents one of three colorways that make up a stylish collection inspired by the British fashion designer’s latex stockings. The lifestyle runner’s sock-like upper is enveloped in a seamless orange shroud, made with semi-translucent TPU and equipped with a webbing pull tab and zip closure for easy on and off. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a two-tone FLYTEFOAM Propel midsole, enhanced with ASICS’ Gel technology in the heel.

results.name: Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bull Red 2021 (PS)
results.story: Crafted for little kids, this 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 5 Retro PS ‘Raging Bull’ brings back one-half of the coveted Defining Moments Pack from 2009. A rich crimson hue floods the suede upper, accented with molded black eyelets and translucent netting on the quarter panel. ‘23’ is embroidered on the lateral heel, while Jumpman branding adorns the back heel and reflective silver tongue. The mid-top is mounted on a black foam midsole with signature shark-tooth detailing in white.

results.name: Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bull Red 2021 (GS)
results.story: Built for big kids, the 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 5 Retro GS ‘Raging Bull’ brings back one-half of the ‘Raging Bull’ Pack from 2009. Soft suede in a bold crimson hue is utilized on the upper, accented with translucent quarter panel netting and black molded eyelets. Jumpman branding adorns the heel, reflective silver tongue and icy rubber outsole. Additional embellishments include a ‘23’ on the lateral heel and red-tipped shark tooth detailing on the contrasting black midsole.

results.name: Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bull Red (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Raging Bull’ brings back a beloved colorway originally released as one-half of 2009’s Air Jordan 5 Raging Bulls Pack. The shoe’s defining feature is a plush Varsity Red suede upper, equipped with black eyelets and a Jumpman-branded reflective silver tongue. The heel overlay displays a second Jumpman logo and an embroidered 23 on the lateral side. A visible Nike Air heel unit enhances the polyurethane midsole, accented with red-tipped shark tooth detailing and supported by an icy translucent outsole.

results.name: Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bull Red 2021 (TD)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 5 Retro TD ‘Raging Bull’ brings back scaled-down version of a coveted colorway originally released in 2009 as part of a two-piece Defining Moments Pack. The mid-top is dressed in a soft suede upper in a deep scarlet hue. This toddler’s version comes complete with translucent quarter-panel netting, an embroidered ‘23’ on the lateral heel and Jumpman branding on the reflective silver tongue. A contrasting black foam midsole is embellished with signature shark tooth detailing in a solid white finish.

results.name: Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit 'Black'
results.story: The Pharrell x adidas Superstar Primeknit ‘Black’ delivers the visionary creative’s interpretation of the classic silhouette. Traditional leather construction is replaced by flexible Primeknit, complete with woven detailing that replicates the look of the iconic shell toe. The all-black finish is disrupted by Vivid Green branding hits, including ‘Humanrace’ embroidered on the heel tab and an inverted adidas wordmark on the tongue. The lightweight build is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole.

results.name: LeBron 18 'Best Of 1-9'
results.story: The Nike LeBron 18 ‘Best of 1-9’ gives the hoops shoe a ‘What The’-style makeover, highlighted by a multi-hued design that draws from some of the most celebrated colorways in the history of LBJ’s signature line. Notable examples include: a blue KnitPosite upper with pink laces redolent of the ‘South Beach’ LeBron 8; a pink splatter heel counter inspired by the ‘Hot Lava’ LeBron 16; a pinstriped interior bootie reminiscent of the ‘Yankees’ LeBron 5; and a prismatic rubber outsole that recalls the ‘Fruity Pebbles’ Lebron 4.

results.name: Wild Rider 'Layers - White Ebony'
results.story: Modeled after the Easy Rider 2 OG, the PUMA Wild Rider Layers ‘White Ebony’ highlights pastel accents on a predominantly neutral build. The white nylon upper is lined in yellow terry cloth and reinforced with nubuck overlays in grey and mint green. A PU-coated black leather Formstrip flows past the shaggy suede heel tab, its wraparound back end culminating in a functional pull tab. Lightweight cushioning arrives via an injection-molded EVA midsole.

results.name: 327 'Black Multi'
results.story: The New Balance 327 ‘Black Multi’ updates the retro-inspired silhouette with a color-blocked upper. Black textile is reinforced with suede overlays at the forefoot and heel in contrasting coral and lime green hues. They’re joined by patchwork suede eyestays in turquoise and violet. On the sneaker’s lateral side, an oversized ‘N’ logo takes inspiration from the New Balance 320. Underfoot, the studded rubber outsole is borrowed from another ‘70s silhouette, the 355.

results.name: Air Max 90 Leather GS 'White Turf Orange Speckled'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Air Max 90 Leather GS ‘White Turf Orange Speckled’ features a mostly neutral palette with sharply contrasting accents. Traditional mesh construction is discarded in favor of an all-leather upper in black, white and grey tones. The sneaker’s lower TPU eyelets are rendered in a bright orange hue, matching the waffle-traction rubber outsole. A blue-tinged Max Air unit supplements the speckled foam midsole while also providing a cooling burst of color.

results.name: Wmns SL Andridge 'Glow Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s SL Andridge ‘Glow Pink’ delivers a subtle colorway of a lifestyle silhouette that borrows liberally from ‘70s running shoes. Ghillie-style lacing secures an upper crafted from beige textile with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Matching leather three-stripes are enlivened with exposed zigzag stitching. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole in a blend of EVA and TPU, supported underfoot by a pink-hued rubber outsole.

results.name: Wild Rider 'Layers - White Viridian Green'
results.story: The PUMA Wild Rider Layers ‘White Viridian Green’ highlights vibrant accents on a lifestyle runner that expands the brand’s ‘Futro’ lineup, composed of evolved takes on archival silhouettes. The upper is constructed from white ripstop nylon with forefoot and heel overlays in teal and grey nubuck. Orange terry cloth lines the interior, while a PU-coated black leather Formstrip doubles as a pull tab at the heel. An injection-molded EVA midsole features debossed circles that amplify the sneaker’s retro-futuristic aesthetic.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'Halo Ivory'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Halo Ivory’ updates the iconic silhouette with a tan synthetic leather upper made with 50% recycled content. The sustainable build comes replete with signature Stan Smith details, including tonal stitching, perforated three-stripes and a Trefoil logo stamped on the heel tab. adidas’ Primegreen branding adorns the sockliner, indicating that the shoe contains zero virgin plastic. A standard white rubber cupsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Vivienne Westwood x Gel Kayano 27 LTX 'Black'
results.story: The Vivienne Westwood x ASICS Gel Kayano 27 LTX ‘Black’ highlights a stealthy monochromatic finish on a lifestyle sneaker inspired by the British fashion designer’s latex stockings. A semi-translucent TPU shroud is wrapped around the sock-like upper, featuring zip closure and dual branding on the lateral side. The streamlined build rides on a FLYTEFOAM Propel midsole, fitted with a shock-absorbing Gel insert in the heel and reinforced with a high-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: GV Special 'US Open'
results.story: The PUMA GV Special ‘US Open’ brings back a retro silhouette named after Argentinean tennis great Guillermo Vilas, who hoisted the American Grand Slam trophy in 1977. The mixed-material upper combines a perforated leather toe box with midfoot paneling in white mesh and blue suede. NYC branding lands on the woven tongue tag and heel tab, both rendered in a bright green finish. Underfoot, a translucent herringbone outsole reveals an oversized tennis ball graphic.

results.name: Five Ten Kestrel Pro Boa 'Black Red'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Kestrel Pro Boa ‘Black Red’ treats the mountain biking shoe to stealthy finish and a sustainable build. Recycled materials make up part of the composition of the weather-resistant synthetic upper, secured with a Boa lacing system and adjustable forefoot strap. The sneaker is mounted on a matching black EVA midsole that’s reinforced with a carbon-infused nylon shank. Underfoot, a Stealth C4 rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Broderie'
results.story: Inspired by boho crochet fashion, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Broderie’ wears a cream-hued canvas upper entirely covered in embroidered florals. The subtle texture is accompanied by standard Chuck details, including a rubber toe cap, chrome eyelets and a circular All Star ankle patch. The high-top is mounted on a platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. Black pinstripes and a Converse license plate add recognizable elements to the sneaker’s revamped tooling.

results.name: Chuck 70 Low 'Tri-Panel'
results.story: The Converse Chuck 70 Low ‘Tri-Panel’ treats the iconic silhouette to a color-blocked makeover. On both the left and right shoe, the canvas upper features lime green paneling on the lateral side and powder blue on the medial side. A neutral white finish lands on the tongue and heel overlay. The low-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole, featuring the Chuck 70’s signature glossy sidewalls. Underfoot, a standard brown rubber outsole is equipped with a traditional diamond traction pattern.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Platform Low 'Black Leopard'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Black Leopard’ gives the classic silhouette a fashion-forward look. The low-top is clad in black canvas with leopard-print detailing on the laces and heel overlay. Standard Chuck tooling is replaced by an elevated platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. The raised sidewall is accented with traditional black pinstripes and a Converse license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a brown rubber outsole features a customary diamond tread for durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Cloud Pink'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Cloud Pink’ brings back the OG Speedcat, released in 1981 and inspired by F1 track style. The sneaker’s low-profile pink suede upper is reinforced with a tonal T-toe overlay and accented with a white suede Formstrip. Additional branding hits include PUMA’s jumping cat logo on the lateral toe and heel tab. Underfoot, the black rubber outsole continues the motorsport theme with a herringbone tire tread and rounded driver’s heel.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 'Ghost Pepper Habanero'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 ‘Ghost Pepper Habanero’ showcases warm tones on a rugged silhouette made for long trail runs. The mesh upper is strengthened by incorporating TPU yarns and a Toe Protect overlay that guards against rocks, roots and other debris. A seamless heel counter cradles the back of the foot for enhanced stability, while the traditional lacing system adds integrated lace loops for midfoot lockdown. Lightweight cushioning arrives via Fresh Foam midsole, reinforced by a lugged Vibram outsole.

results.name: adidas City Series Wien Blue Tint
results.story: The adidas Wien SPZL ‘City Series’ brings back an archival silhouette that pays homage to Vienna, Austria. A rich royal blue finish is applied to the soft suede upper, reinforced with a toe overlay and marked with gold-foil ‘Wien’ branding. Contrasting orange accents make their way to the heel tab, serrated three-stripes and leather collar lining, the latter engraved with ‘City Series MMXXI.’ The low-profile lace-up is mounted on a semi-translucent gum rubber cupsole.

results.name: ASICS Gel-Quantam 90 Coca-Cola White
results.story: The Coca-Cola x ASICS Gel Quantum 90 ‘White’ dresses the lifestyle runner in the signature colors of the iconic American beverage brand. The breathable white knit upper is made in part with recycled polyester, while the sockliner is colored with a dope-dyed technique that requires less ink and water. On the lateral side, the Coca-Cola logo is inscribed on the midfoot cage, which doubles as the sneaker’s tiger stripe branding. The lightweight build is supported by a solid white EVA midsole with green-tinged Gel cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Nike Lebron 7 Los Angeles Dodgers
results.story: The Nike LeBron 7 ‘Dodgers’ brings back LeBron James’ seventh signature shoe in a familiar color scheme inspired by LA’s MLB franchise. A crisp white finish is executed on the upper, featuring Flywire-infused synthetic paneling and matching leather overlays. The signature Swoosh is outlined in royal blue, matching the leather mudguard embellished with a tonal palm-leaf print. Red zigzag stitching on the tongue and heel tab is redolent of an official Rawlings baseball.
